						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the Hanumān temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 15 • ., Virōdhikṛit, Vaiśākha, śu • .</p>						

						<p>Damaged and fragmentary. Records the gift of land in the village Mēḍarā of Taṅgeḍa-sīma to the temples of Kēśava-Perumāḷ, Siddhaya, Hanumān and Rudrēśvara at Jānapāḍu for conducting worship.</p>						

						</summary>
